  <span id="freeText595851609338625001" style="display:none">An aging widow is surprised one night by a girl, a deaf man, and their tiny baby, drenched with rain and searching for shelter. The woman doesn't know, but they have escaped an institution for the disabled, and guards are chasing them. Soon these lives change dramatically, and we follow them, desperately hoping their paths cross again. This was both deeply wrenching and satisfying.<br /><br />I both listened and read this. Wonderful narration.</span>
